{"type":"message","id":"f1395391","parentId":"17e181b2","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:00:52.787Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我注意到没有专门的\"通讯录\"技能。但实际上，通过飞书 API 的一些用户信息获取功能可能已经包含在现有的工具中了。\n\n让我再仔细看一下有哪些与用户/通讯录相关的工具可用：\n\n1. `feishu_search_user` - 搜索员工（通过关键词）\n2. `feishu_get_user` - 获取用户信息\n\n这些工具可能需要特定的权限才能工作。让我看看飞书开放平台 API 是否提供了获取通讯录的 API。\n\n根据飞书开发文档，获取通讯录通常需要以下权限：\n- contact:user.base:readonly - 读取用户基本信息\n- contact:user.id:readonly - 读取用户 user_id\n- contact:department.base:readonly - 读取部门基本信息\n\n让我先尝试用 get_user 获取当前用户信息，看看是否能工作：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l33be6805tuo_1","name":"feishu_get_user","arguments":{}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":312,"output":185,"cacheRead":37885,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38382,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773648046281}}
{"type":"message","id":"3a084e24","parentId":"f1395391","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:00:53.589Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_l33be6805tuo_1","toolName":"feishu_get_user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"user\": {\n    \"avatar_big\": \"https://s3-imfile.feishucdn.com/static-resource/v1/v3_00sr_757d88bb-79d9-4590-bd71-07916689abfg~?image_size=640x640&cut_type=&quality=&format=image&sticker_format=.webp\",\n    \"avatar_middle\": \"https://s1-imfile.feishucdn.com/static-resource/v1/v3_00sr_757d88bb-79d9-4590-bd71-07916689abfg~?image_size=240x240&cut_type=&quality=&format=image&sticker_format=.webp\",\n    \"avatar_thumb\": \"https://s1-imfile.feishucdn.com/static-resource/v1/v3_00sr_757d88bb-79d9-4590-bd71-07916689abfg~?image_size=72x72&cut_type=&quality=&format=image&sticker_format=.webp\",\n    \"avatar_url\": \"https://s1-imfile.feishucdn.com/static-resource/v1/v3_00sr_757d88bb-79d9-4590-bd71-07916689abfg~?image_size=72x72&cut_type=&quality=&format=image&sticker_format=.webp\",\n    \"en_name\": \"姚霖\",\n    \"name\": \"姚霖\",\n    \"open_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n    \"tenant_key\": \"1065220fab165740\",\n    \"union_id\": \"on_42fdfd07c1033b1c0f054ff0e3904ed8\",\n    \"user_id\": \"b622a7b8\"\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"user":{"avatar_big":"https://s3-imfile.feishucdn.com/static-resource/v1/v3_00sr_757d88bb-79d9-4590-bd71-07916689abfg~?image_size=640x640&cut_type=&quality=&format=image&sticker_format=.webp","avatar_middle":"https://s1-imfile.feishucdn.com/static-resource/v1/v3_00sr_757d88bb-79d9-4590-bd71-07916689abfg~?image_size=240x240&cut_type=&quality=&format=image&sticker_format=.webp","avatar_thumb":"https://s1-imfile.feishucdn.com/static-resource/v1/v3_00sr_757d88bb-79d9-4590-bd71-07916689abfg~?image_size=72x72&cut_type=&quality=&format=image&sticker_format=.webp","avatar_url":"https://s1-imfile.feishucdn.com/static-resource/v1/v3_00sr_757d88bb-79d9-4590-bd71-07916689abfg~?image_size=72x72&cut_type=&qual