{"type":"message","id":"4d0ebd6c","parentId":"79ecca73","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:02:01.054Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要开通通讯录的全部权限。我需要帮助用户了解如何开通飞书通讯录权限。\n\n让我先查看飞书开放平台的相关信息，看看需要什么权限，然后在文档中搜索如何获取通讯录权限。\n\n首先，我需要了解飞书通讯录权限的具体内容。让我查看一下相关的技能或文档。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我先查看一下飞书通讯录权限的相关信息，然后帮你配置。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yvh46744ksh1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://open.feishu.cn/document/server-docs/contact-api-v3/permission-scope/permission-description\" 2>/dev/null | head -50"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":3493,"output":139,"cacheRead":35069,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38701,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773648110046}}
