{"type":"message","id":"ee090cca","parentId":"0c6be0da","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:16:32.293Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来返回的用户信息中没有生日字段。飞书的通讯录API可能需要额外的权限才能获取生日信息。让我检查一下需要什么权限才能获取生日。\n\n根据飞书开放平台的文档，获取用户生日需要 `contact:user.birthday:readonly` 权限。\n\n让我告诉用户这个情况。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_f667aryj7eqb_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://open.feishu.cn/document/server-docs/contact-api-v3/user-description/user-get\" 2>/dev/null | grep -i birthday || echo \"No birthday info found\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":616,"output":127,"cacheRead":47101,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47844,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773648987472}}
