{"type":"message","id":"c69f60c1","parentId":"8c90d6dc","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:16:45.196Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来当前的飞书API没有返回生日信息。根据飞书开放平台的文档，获取用户生日需要额外的权限 `contact:user.birthday:readonly`。我需要告诉用户这个情况。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"抱歉，目前**无法查看员工生日信息**。\n\n## 问题\n\n飞书的通讯录 API 需要额外权限才能获取生日：\n- 权限名称：`contact:user.birthday:readonly`\n\n目前我的工具返回的用户信息中**没有生日字段**。\n\n---\n\n## 解决方案\n\n你需要在飞书开放平台后台**开通这个权限**：\n1. 进入 https://open.feishu.cn/\n2. 找到你的应用 → 权限管理 → API 权限\n3. 搜索 `contact:user.birthday:readonly` 并开通\n\n需要我去帮你开通这个权限吗？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":251,"output":165,"cacheRead":47613,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48029,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773648992426}}
{"type":"message","id":"26be3bb5","parentId":"c69f60c1","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:17:00.066Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-16 16:16:59 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b [msg:om_x100b544f8963e0a8c3ff50f762beb4a]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b544f8963e0a8c3ff50f762beb4a\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-16 16:16 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_d75c71eb9cc3369175d62f2892cd7b8b\"\n}\n```\n\n开通该权限"}],"timestamp":1773649020064}}
{"type":"message","id":"918e0d01","parentId":"26be3bb5","timestamp":"2026-03-16T08:17:11.310Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我开通生日权限。但我无法直接在飞书开放平台后台开通权限，这需要用户手动操作。我需要告诉用户如何开通这个权限。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我无法直接在代码中开通这个权限，需要**你去飞书开放平台手动开通**。\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 开通生日权限步骤\n\n1. 打开 https://open.feishu.cn/ 并登录\n2. 进入「应用开发」→ 选择你的应用\n3. 点击「权限管理」→ 「API 权限」\n4. 搜索 `contact:user.birthday:readonly` \n5. 点击「开通」\n\n---\n\n开通完成后告诉我，我再帮你查询员工生日信息！🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":1826,"output":139,"cacheRead":46333,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48298,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773649020065}}
